#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kfontview; is an application to view and install different types of fonts:"
msgstr "&kfontview; je aplikacija za ogled in namestitev različnih vrst pisav:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "&TrueType; (<filename class=\"extension\">.ttf</filename>)"
msgstr "&TrueType; (<filename class=\"extension\">.ttf</filename>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"OpenType (<filename class=\"extension\">otf</filename>, <filename class="
"\"extension\">.ttf</filename>)"
msgstr ""
"OpenType (Odprti tip) (<filename class=\"extension\">otf</filename>, "
"<filename class=\"extension\">.ttf</filename>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&PostScript; type 1 (file extension on &Windows; &amp; OS/2 <filename class="
"\"extension\">.pfb</filename>/<filename class=\"extension\">.pfm</filename>; "
"on &UNIX;/&Linux; <filename class=\"extension\">.pfa</filename>/<filename "
"class=\"extension\">.afm</filename>)"
msgstr ""
"&PostScript; tip 1 (razširitev datoteke na &Windows; &amp; OS/2 <filename "
"class=\"extension\">.pfb</filename>/<filename class=\"extension\">.pfm</"
"filename>; na &UNIX;/&Linux; <filename class=\"extension\">.pfa</filename>/"
"<filename class=\"extension\">.afm</filename>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"BDF (Bitmap Distribution Format, file extension <filename class=\"extension"
"\">.bdf</filename>)"
msgstr ""
"BDF (Bitmap Distribution Format, podaljšek datoteke <filename class="
"\"extension\">.bdf</filename>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"PCF (Portable Compiled Format, file extension <filename class=\"extension\">."
"pcf</filename>)"
msgstr ""
"PCF (Portable Compiled Format, podaljšek datoteke <filename class=\"extension"
"\">.pcf</filename>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use it as standalone program to preview and install a font "
"downloaded from the Internet. In the preview you can check that the font has "
"all characters you need."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite jo lahko kot samostojen program za predogled in namestitev pisave, "
"prenesene iz interneta. V predogledu lahko preverite, ali ima pisava vse "
"znake, ki jih potrebujete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &kfontview; can be launched from the &systemsettings; module "
"<ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/fontinst/index.html\"> <guilabel>Font "
"Management</guilabel></ulink> to use the extended preview capabilities of "
"&kfontview;."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega lahko &kfontview; zaženete iz modula &systemsettings; <ulink url="
"\"help:/kcontrol/fontinst/index.html\"> <guilabel>Upravljanje pisav</"
"guilabel></ulink>, da uporabite razširjene zmožnosti predogleda &kfontview;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alternatively you can use the <guilabel>Font Management</guilabel> module to "
"install, remove, preview and manage all fonts on your system."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite lahko tudi modul <guilabel>Upravljanje pisav</guilabel> za "
"namestitev, odstranitev, predogled in upravljanje vseh pisav v sistemu."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kfontview; application</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kfontview; aplikacija</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kfontview; application</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kfontview; aplikacija</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kfontview;'s <guilabel>Standard Preview</guilabel> displays your font in "
"several different sizes using a pangram (a sentence using every letter of "
"the alphabet at least once). So you can get a good idea of what it will look "
"like. From the drop down box in the toolbar you can choose additional "
"preview types:"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Standardni predogled</guilabel> prikaže vašo pisavo v več "
"različnih velikostih z uporabo pangrama (stavek, v katerem je vsaka črka "
"abecede uporabljena vsaj enkrat). Tako si lahko ustvarite dobro predstavo o "
"tem, kako bo videti. V spustnem oknu v orodni vrstici lahko izberete dodatne "
"vrste predogleda:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>All Characters</guilabel> displays all characters provided by the "
"font in one size."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Vsi znaki</guilabel> prikaže vse znake, ki jih zagotavlja pisava, "
"v eni velikosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unicode Block: The Unicode standard arranges groups of characters together "
"in blocks"
msgstr "Blok Unicode: Standard Unicode skupine znakov razvršča v bloke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unicode Script: In Unicode, a script is a collection of letters and other "
"written signs used to represent textual information in one or more writing "
"systems"
msgstr ""
"Skripta Unicode: V Unicode je skripta zbirka črk in drugih pisnih znakov, ki "
"se uporabljajo za predstavitev besedilnih informacij v enem ali več pisnih "
"sistemih"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Change Text</guibutton>: Using this button opens the "
"<guilabel>Preview String</guilabel> dialog where you can insert a user "
"defined text. This feature enables you to check that a font supports the "
"characters you need."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Spremeni besedilo</guibutton>: Z uporabo tega gumba se odpre "
"pogovorno okno <guilabel>Predogled niza</guilabel>, v katerega lahko "
"vstavite uporabniško določeno besedilo. S to funkcijo lahko preverite, ali "
"pisava podpira znake, ki jih potrebujete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use the zoom buttons or the mousewheel to change the font size in "
"all preview types."
msgstr ""
"Za spreminjanje velikosti pisave v vseh vrstah predogledov lahko uporabite "
"gumbe za povečavo ali kolesce miške."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In <guilabel>Unicode Block</guilabel> and <guilabel>Unicode Script</"
"guilabel> preview mode additional tooltip info's are displayed hovering a "
"character with the mouse pointer: The character's Unicode "
"<guilabel>Category</guilabel> and the value in <guilabel> UCS-4</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>UTF-16</guilabel>, <guilabel>UTF-8</guilabel> and as <guilabel>XML "
"Decimal Entity</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"V načinu predogleda <guilabel>Blok Unicode</guilabel> in <guilabel>Skripta "
"Unicode</guilabel> se prikažejo dodatne informacije v obliki namiga orodja, "
"če znak obesite s kazalcem miške: Unicode <guilabel>Kategorija </guilabel> "
"znaka in vrednost v <guilabel> UCS-4</guilabel>, <guilabel>UTF-16</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>UTF-8</guilabel> in kot <guilabel>XML Decimal Entity</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To install a font you downloaded from the Internet, click the "
"<guibutton>Install</guibutton> button in the lower-right corner."
msgstr ""
"Če želite namestiti pisavo, ki ste jo prenesli z interneta, kliknite gumb "
"<guibutton>Namesti</guibutton> v spodnjem desnem kotu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can install the font for personal us only available to you or system-"
"wide available for all users, the latter will require administrator "
"privileges."
msgstr ""
"Pisavo lahko namestite za osebno rabo, ki je na voljo samo vam, ali za "
"celoten sistem, ki je na voljo vsem uporabnikom; za slednje so potrebni "
"skrbniški privilegiji."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Fonts are often provided in an archive format like <literal role=\"extension"
"\">zip</literal>. Open these archives with &ark; which provides a simple "
"previewer for fonts. To make use of the extended capabilities of &kfontview; "
"extract the fonts and open them in &kfontview;."
msgstr ""
"Pisave so pogosto na voljo v obliki arhiva, kot je <literal role=\"extension"
"\">zip</literal>. Te arhive odprite s programom &ark;, ki omogoča preprost "
"predogled pisav. Če želite izkoristiti razširjene zmogljivosti programa "
"&kfontview;, izberite pisave in jih odprite v programu &kfontview;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "Applications need to be restarted to use of the newly installed fonts."
msgstr "Za uporabo novo nameščenih pisav je treba znova zagnati aplikacije."
